ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I do not think that the incoming graduate students will have a choice on whether or not they can take the course. In any case, I did enjoy my time in the course.

Reading proposals from varied subject areas and making difficult decisions about which should be funded with very limited resources. An excellent learning exercise for those curious about how the NSF works

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Through this course, I was able to learn more about the grant review process. I was also able to learn more about the faculty in the department and their interests.
better understanding about how the NSF works
